### âœ… Snort Setup and Rules

- Installed Snort on Kali Linux:
 
sudo apt update
sudo apt install snort
snort -V
sudo snort -A console -i eth0 -c /etc/snort/snort.conf
alert icmp any any -> any any (msg:"ICMP Packet Detected"; sid:1000001; rev:1;)
